    "%load_ext autoreload\n",
    "%autoreload 2\n",
    "import wavesight as ws\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from matplotlib import pyplot as plt\n",
    "from scipy import special"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## ## Step-index modes"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 101,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "0.011510107015457788"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 101,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "(nCore**2 - nCladding**2)/2/nCore**2"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Estimating nCladding from nCore and NA ...\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1000x200 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fiber_spec = {'NA': 0.22,\n",
    "              'nCore': 1.45,\n",
    "              'coreRadius':25.,\n",
    "              'grid_divider': 2,\n",
    "              'nFree': 1.,\n",
    "              'λFree': 0.600}\n",
    "nCore = fiber_spec['nCore']\n",
    "if 'NA' in fiber_spec:\n",
    "    print(\"Estimating nCladding from nCore and NA ...\")\n",
    "    NA        = fiber_spec['NA']\n",
    "    nCladding = np.sqrt(nCore**2 - NA**2)\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    nCladding = fiber_spec['nCladding']\n",
    "    NA        =  np.sqrt(nCore**2 - nCladding**2)\n",
    "# nCladding = 1.01\n",
    "coreRadius    = fiber_spec['coreRadius']\n",
    "wavelength    = fiber_spec['λFree']\n",
    "λFree         = wavelength\n",
    "kzmax         = nCore * 2 * np.pi / wavelength\n",
    "kzmin         = nCladding * 2 *np.pi / wavelength\n",
    "kzspan        = kzmax - kzmin\n",
    "kzmax         = kzmax - 0.001 * kzspan\n",
    "kzmin         = kzmin + 0.001 * kzspan\n",
    "# split the solution domain in at least 300 parts\n",
    "dkz           = (kzmax - kzmin) / 300\n",
    "sol           = fiber_spec\n",
    "Vnum          = 2 * np.pi * coreRadius * NA / wavelength\n",
    "sol['Vnum']   = Vnum\n",
    "numModes      = int(Vnum**2/2)\n",
    "numModesTE    = int(Vnum/2)\n",
    "numModesTM    = int(Vnum/2)\n",
    "numModesHE    = int(Vnum*(Vnum-2)/4)\n",
    "ω             = 2*np.pi / λFree\n",
    "m = 2\n",
    "tmfun = ws.tmfungen(λfree = wavelength, \n",
    "                    n2 = nCladding, \n",
    "                    n1 = nCore, \n",
    "                        a = coreRadius)\n",
    "tefun = ws.tefungen(λfree = wavelength, \n",
    "                    n2 = nCladding, \n",
    "                    n1 = nCore, \n",
    "                        a = coreRadius)\n",
    "hefun = ws.hefungen(λfree = wavelength, \n",
    "                    m = m,\n",
    "                    n2 = nCladding, \n",
    "                    n1 = nCore, \n",
    "                        a = coreRadius)\n",
    "dkzprime = dkz/numModesTE/100\n",
    "real_dtype = np.float64\n",
    "tmmodes = ws.findallroots(tmfun, kzmin, kzmax, dkzprime, \n",
    "                    dtype=real_dtype, method='brentq', num_sigfigs=10)\n",
    "kzrange = np.linspace(kzmin, kzmax, 1000, dtype=real_dtype)\n",
    "\n",
    "thebessel = lambda x: special.jv(m, coreRadius*np.sqrt(nCore**2 * ω**2 - x**2))\n",
    "thebessel = np.vectorize(thebessel)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10,2))\n",
    "plt.plot(kzrange, tmfun(kzrange), 'c', label='TM')\n",
    "plt.plot([kzrange[0], kzrange[-1]], [0,0], 'w:')\n",
    "plt.plot(tmmodes, tmfun(tmmodes), 'ro', label='TM roots')\n",
    "plt.ylim(-1,1)\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
